  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00052', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-112-707b521e', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-05', NULL, 'essay', '某市為配合高科技產業的升級及轉型，提升生活機能與區域生活，針對
